1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
[INSIDE SPACESHIP - NIGHT]
[Sound of intermittent alarm]
[MARK]  [Scared] What the hell...?

2
00:00:03,500 --> 00:00:06,000
[Mark jumps out of bed and runs towards the control panel]
[Sound of heavy footsteps]

3
00:00:06,500 --> 00:00:09,000
[Control panel]  [Flashing lights] Critical life support system!

4
00:00:09,500 --> 00:00:12,000
[Mark]  [Sweaty, worried]  I need to fix this fast!

5
00:00:12,500 --> 00:00:15,000
[Mark starts pressing buttons frantically]
[Sound of buttons being pressed]

6
00:00:15,500 --> 00:00:18,000
[Mark]  [Frustrated]  Damn it!

7
00:00:18,500 --> 00:00:21,000
[Sound of louder alarm]
[Mark]  [Fear]  No, no, no!

8
00:00:21,500 --> 00:00:24,000
[Mark looks out the window]
[Outer space]  [Twinkling stars]  I'm all alone...

9
00:00:24,500 --> 00:00:27,000
[Mark sits down and rests his head in his hands]
[Sound of deep breath]

10
00:00:27,500 --> 00:00:30,000
[Mark]  [Determined]  I can do this. I have to find a solution.

11
00:00:30,500 --> 00:00:33,000
[Mark gets up and starts working on the control panel again]
[Sound of buttons being pressed]

12
00:00:33,500 --> 00:00:36,000
[Control panel]  [Lights turn off, then back on]  System restored!

13
00:00:36,500 --> 00:00:39,000
[Mark]  [Relief]  I did it!

14
00:00:39,500 --> 00:00:42,000
[Sound of a relaxing melody]
[Mark smiles and looks out the window]

15
00:00:42,500 --> 00:00:45,000
[Outer space]  [Colorful nebula]  What a view!

16
00:00:45,500 --> 00:00:48,000
[Mark takes a notebook and a pen]
[Sound of pages turning]

17
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:51,000
[Mark starts writing]
[Mark's thought]  [Internal voice]  I have to write this all down...

18
00:00:51,500 --> 00:00:54,000
[Mark smiles]
[Mark's thought]  [Internal voice]  Who would have thought?

19
00:00:54,500 --> 00:00:57,000
[Final scene: Mark looks at Earth from the window]
[Earth]  [Small blue dot]  Home...

20
00:00:57,500 --> 00:00:60,000
[Sound of a nostalgic melody]